results.description:
De tweedejaars Communication & Multimedia Design (IxD/UXD) studenten presenteren hun creatieve en innovatieve installaties waarbij techniek centraal staat. Kom langs en ervaar Augmented & Virtual Reality, Wearable Technology, Exertion Games en Artifical Creatures!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

The second year students Communication & Multimedia Design (iXD/UXD) are presenting their creative and innovative installations. Visit the expo and experience Augmented & Virtual Reality, Wearable Technology, Exertion Games en Artifical Creatures first hand!
